<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Error — METICS</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" />
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .header-bar {
            background-color: #095998;
            height: 95px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
        }
        .error-card {
            max-width: 540px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #095998;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="flex-grow-1 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center py-5">
        <div class="error-card text-center px-4">
            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-circle error-icon mb-3 d-block"></i>
            <h1 class="h3 fw-bold text-dark mb-2">Ocurrió un problema</h1>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                Lo sentimos, algo salió mal al procesar su solicitud.<br />
                Si el problema persiste, comuníquese con el equipo de soporte.
            </p>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary px-4" style="background-color: #095998; border-color: #095998;">
                <i class="bi bi-house-door me-2"></i>Volver al inicio
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="text-center text-muted py-3" style="font-size: 0.85rem;">
        &copy; @DateTime.Now.Year METICS — Universidad de Costa Rica
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
